sources.title: TOMBSTONE CANYON Ken Maynard
sources.description: In search of the identity of his parents, Ken Mason (Ken Maynard) rides through Tombstone Canyon to meet a man who has information about them. When strangers fire on Ken, he is rescued by Jenny Lee (Cecelia Parker). Upon finding the man he was to meet murdered, Ken learns about the Phantom, who stal ks the canyon but only attacks people associated with the outlaw Alf Sykes. Interested in remaining near Jenny, Ken takes up impersonating the Phantom to unearth the mystery of his heritage.
